# Cursor Rules for Frontend App - French Translation

## General Rules
- Always translate all user-facing text from English to French
- Maintain consistent French terminology throughout the application
- Use proper French grammar and punctuation
- Keep technical terms and variable names in English
- Preserve the original meaning and context

