## Implementation Notes
- Update all hardcoded strings in components
- Update error messages and notifications
- Update form labels and placeholders
- Update button text and action labels
- Update status display text
- Keep console.log messages in English for debugging
- Keep variable names, function names, and technical terms in English
- Use proper French quotation marks (« ») where appropriate
- Maintain consistent capitalization rules for French

## File Types to Update
- React components (.tsx, .jsx)
- TypeScript files (.ts)
- CSS files with text content
- Configuration files with user-facing text
- README files and documentation 